snippet.title: Toribash (WiiWare) 1 Turn Judo Decap
snippet.description:
Judo Tutorial Series 1
This vid shows you how to decap your opponent in 1 turn in Judo.
If you're new to Toribash, it's important to learn how force is generated within the body.
Rotate your pecs and sternum to gain torque and hit harder.
More at blog.toribash.com
